				"geo_event_type": "location",
				"data": {
					"geo_event_type": "location",
					"location_type": "animal_shelter",
					"information": "<p>Any evacuated pets can be brought to the <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" href=\"https://app.watchduty.org/location/45512\">evacuation shelter</a> or at Aransas County Animal Care Services at 872 Airport Rd, Rockport, TX 78382, per <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/permalink.php?story_fbid=pfbid02nW4KEPKV3N829yYouuVXromo3mSThw8HQwzxvXjxjAW1DYYt2nJJupszYXGLEKNvl&amp;id=100064902151572\">Rockport Public Safety Center on Facebook</a>.</p><p>For animals brought to Aransas County Animal Care Services&nbsp;that are not dogs or cats, please bring containments for them per <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/actxanimalcare/posts/pfbid0unV1PXXuQgpcSZ8c8rtY4koKpiznAQRyWvaxXe5BpF3N3741an6DTY2T9vZzcEKtl\">their Facebook page</a>. Call 361-790-0151 if you need assistance.</p>",
